data.rationale:
provides a function to calculate the postal charges for SwissPost
    services to any country in the world, for economy, priority or
    urgent serices. Includes translation from ISO6166 country identifier
    to SwissPost zone, listing of available services to the zone and
    pricing up to 30kg for each zone and SwissPost service.

    Similar modules can be developed for other postal services (eg
    USPS, Royal Mail) using a common API.

    Inspired by the shipping modules built into OsCommerce
    (http://www.oscommerce.org) ..
